"Who is the man that play Roots, Rock, Reggae? Michael Campbell... And who is the rock with the rock on the rock ? It's the Dread At The Control... Michael Campbell to thrill your soul !"

Michael George Campbell (born 4 June 1954 in Port Antonio, Jamaica - died 15 March 2008 in Connecticut, United States),better known as Mikey Dread, was a Jamaican singer, producer, and broadcaster. He was one of the most influential performers and innovators in reggae music.
